This paper is primarily focused on computer vision and machine learning techniques for face tracking, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper extensively uses deep learning models for face detection, verification, and tracking, which makes it likely to be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as well. The paper also deals with multimedia analysis and retrieval, which can be categorized under multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
